						li: p For the Safari web browser, please visit this page from Apple: 
							a(href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac", target="_blank") https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac
						li: p For any other web browser, please visit your web browser's official web pages.
